getDecimals(address).details: Returns the asset's number of decimals

getStableCoinAddress().details: Returns the address of the stable coin

returns._0: uint Price of the asset in USD

getVerifier(address).details: Given the address of an asset, returns the address of the asset's verifier

returns._0: bool Whether the asset is supported
